Class message

java.lang.Object
  com.github.bjarneh.utilz.message

public class message
extends Object

Wrapper functions for Java's MessageDigest library. note: There is a lot of comments here since this is meant to be a library with some documentation, i.e. make sure you turn on your comment folding before you start reading this file.

public static byte[] digest(byte[] b,
                            String algorithm)
                     throws IOException,

Compute a security hash of an array of bytes. This function is basically just a wrapper for the standard library MessageDigest methods.

Parameters:
b - bytes to base the hash on
algorithm - which message digest algorithm to use

IOException
